## Approach

### Traditional Approach
```
Full Scene Download â†’ Local Storage â†’ Process â†’ Result
     ~720 MB            Disk I/O      Slow      
```

### GeoMind Approach (Zarr + fsspec)
```
HTTP Range Request â†’ Stream Chunks â†’ Process in Memory â†’ Result
     ~1-5 MB           No disk          Fast           
```
